{"tid":1905240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢醫院伙食太好 導致患者痛風發作","createTime":"2020-03-01T06:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T15:37:06.000Z","uid":89543,"like":251,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a0e77378bb0b4ecd3a39f8c7ef86a0e47390ab","tid":1905240,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StHHCLP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStHHCLP.png&h=4bedc240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FsfFprb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsfFprb.png&h=d526c382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩岸新聞<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎：爆方艙醫院伙食太好　致患者痛風發作<br />\n湖北武漢因應新冠肺炎疫情嚴重，特別在市內開設多家方艙醫院，專門收治輕症患者<span style=\"color: red;\">。繼早前內媒報道有患者讚醫院伙食豐富，擔心變胖，近日有武漢醫生在社交網稱，有患者因醫院伙食太好，導致痛風發作，惹來網民熱議稱，「治療痛風可不能免費」。</span><br />\n<br />\n華中科技大學同濟醫學院一名骨科醫生在微博發文，表示已有3名病人因痛風發作需轉院接受治療，又附上多張圖片，顯示醫院伙食大魚大肉，包括有豬肉、五香牛肉、蝦仁等<span style=\"color: red;\">，質疑病人因吃得好，沒有消化，致尿酸結晶體都沉澱到腳上，引發痛風。</span><br />\n<br />\n發文引來網民留言，指病人「美食當前沒忍住」；亦有人認為病人需為自己負責，不能怪醫院，因為「醫院有給糖尿病人準備無糖餐」。"},{"pid":"96142d1f2219f9d48fb76ae4227a3e5946ed0f22","tid":1905240,"uid":89543,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200301/mobile/bkn-20200301103131003-0301_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200301%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200301103131003-0301_00952_001.html&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=27cfab09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200301/mobile/bkn-20200301103131003-0301_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"38cd6f3da6314f7642bb5abe522923606c590688","tid":1905240,"uid":89543,"like":440,"dislike":2,"score":438,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"飛機打到上外太空都係第一次見<img src=\"/assets/face